      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUMMER QUINN (1) has a strong record this trip with 13 wins and 14 placings from 37 starts. Comes off a (25.31) win last time, scoring by a nose in a NG over 450m at Grafton. Looks the one to beat with even luck. CUMBRIA BENNY (2) is worth forgiving for his last effort when sixth (30.03) at this track over 520m. Form at the trip sound including eight wins. Has a solid record from this box including three wins and a minor placing. Can figure in the finish. TEXAS BANDIT (3) was a blistering 29.56 winner at this track last start. Expected to feature again. KING OF GODS (4) gets a chance to redeem an unplaced effort here last start.",
